      "content": "i dont even know what to do anymore. everything i spent the last 5 years building is just gone. the company is dead and the debt... i can't even look at the numbers anymore. i feel like a complete joke. how am i supposed to go back and tell my family i blew everything? i just cant face the shame of it.",
