    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding sounds impossible though. it's not just a bad month or a setback, it's everything. the debt is going to follow me forever. i feel like i've fundamentally broken things for everyone around me. i look in the mirror and i don't even see a person anymore, just a mistake. it feels like there's no way to actually fix this or make the shame go away.",
